---
// Privacy Policy Page for HMR Sport Solutions
---

<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | HMR Sport Solutions</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon-32x32.png" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:wght@900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-surface text-on-surface antialiased font-body">
    <header class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-[#eefcfc]/90 dark:bg-[#032829]/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-outline-variant/10">
      <nav class="flex justify-between items-center w-full px-6 lg:px-12 py-4 lg:py-6 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary hover:opacity-70 transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-xl leading-none -mt-1">←</span> Back to Home
        </a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-16 md:pb-24 px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <section class="mb-12 md:mb-16">
          <span class="font-label text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-primary block mb-4 uppercase">Legal</span>
          <h1 class="font-archivo text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.05] md:leading-[0.95] text-primary mb-6 md:mb-8">
            Privacy Policy
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            HMR Sport Solutions respects your privacy and handles personal information with care.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/60 mt-4">Last updated: 6 April 2026</p>
        </section>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-12 border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-8 md:pt-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest">Our Commitment</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-10 md:space-y-12">
            <section>
              <h2 class="font-archivo text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-on-surface mb-3 md:mb-4">What I collect</h2>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                If you contact me through the website form, I may collect your name, organisation, email address, and the message you submit.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="font-archivo text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-on-surface mb-3 md:mb-4">Why I collect it</h2>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                I collect this information so I can respond to your enquiry, communicate with you about potential advisory work, and keep a record of enquiries received through the website.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h2 class="font-archivo text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-on-surface mb-3 md:mb-4">Storage and security</h2>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Information submitted may be stored using service providers like Google Workspace and website hosting tools. I take reasonable steps to protect personal information from loss or unauthorised access.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="p-6 md:p-8 bg-surface-container-low border border-outline-variant/10 rounded-sm">
              <h2 class="font-archivo text-xl md:text-2xl font-black text-on-surface mb-3 md:mb-4">Contact</h2>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-4 md:mb-6 text-base md:text-lg">
                If you have any privacy questions or would like to request access to your information, please contact:
              </p>
              <p class="font-bold text-on-surface">Hamish Rogers</p>
              <a href="mailto:hamish@hmrsportsolutions.co" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline break-all">hamish@hmrsportsolutions.co</a>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="py-10 md:py-12 px-6 lg:px-12 border-t border-outline-variant/10 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant opacity-60">HMR Sport Solutions © {new Date().getFullYear()}</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
  .font-archivo { font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif; }
</style>
